Package: openneuro
Title: Programmatic Access to OpenNeuro Datasets
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Bradley", "Buchsbaum", email = "brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Author: Bradley Buchsbaum [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Bradley Buchsbaum <brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com>
Description: Search, explore, and download datasets from OpenNeuro, the largest
    open neuroimaging repository. Provides GraphQL-based discovery,
    multi-backend downloads (HTTPS/S3/DataLad), and smart caching.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
